    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A return to Classic Survival Horror. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35 days since the terrorist attack - after being hospitalized your Nightmares keep getting more vivid, effects in the Nightmare start affecting your real body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retracing events is the only way to wake up. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/0c2807a1b1ffa402ae40f1f5fc697ecd.webp?t=1733011545\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They've been consistent - find out and perform whatever tasks you did that day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's never mattered how or when, but you won't wake up until they're all done. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/cd724a3c1325a18c5dcb8265e7590a75.poster.avif?t=1733011545\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/cd724a3c1325a18c5dcb8265e7590a75.webm?t=1733011545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/cd724a3c1325a18c5dcb8265e7590a75.mp4?t=1733011545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/4be6b60cb1ec6ec2d2e6304c4ea05247.webp?t=1733011545\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collecting your thoughts is difficult here, thinking out loud can help put things in perspective. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or maybe just touch it, can you open it? Can you even move it? You won't know unless you try.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/c08a943a1ccfe75f0dcad65ce090354d.poster.avif?t=1733011545\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/c08a943a1ccfe75f0dcad65ce090354d.webm?t=1733011545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/c08a943a1ccfe75f0dcad65ce090354d.mp4?t=1733011545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/5c7abb595b04e9acc74fad4dda887093.webp?t=1733011545\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guns are hollow, bricks are immovable - Knives are the only thing that feels real in here. The last time you tried to hold 2, you woke up with half your hand open, make sure 1 hand is always free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/63acba3e3a602d18a1df9db6a0b37a64.poster.avif?t=1733011545\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/63acba3e3a602d18a1df9db6a0b37a64.webm?t=1733011545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294200/extras/63acba3e3a602d18a1df9db6a0b37a64.mp4?t=1733011545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Openly explore the first area of the game, solve the first set of puzzles, find hidden secrets.</p>",
